{"id":212386,"type":6,"name":"ドラゴン青年団","rating":{"total":1,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5},"summary":"　　某天，东京铁塔上突然出现一条西方传说里的飞龙，它盘桓良久，引起大范围的恐慌。远离首都圈的富士山下，坐落着发展缓慢、人丁寥落的光山町，无所事事的青年Yoshio（安田章大 饰）、Kenji（远藤要 饰）终日泡在Youko（莲佛美沙子 饰）的咖啡馆里，事不关己地看着飞龙的新闻。偶然机会，Yoshio意外从旧书店发现一个有着古老历史的卷轴，里面用龙族的文字记载了恶龙和光之战士的故事。他们惊讶地发现，Yoshio、Kenji、Youko以及另一个朋友Tamotsu（本多力 饰）无一例外都有着同样的胎记。莫非他们便是光之战士的后裔？ \r\n　　这一变故让青年们枯燥的生活顿起波澜，他们按图索骥在镇上寻找四枚水晶和圣剑，准备与恶龙一决雌雄…… ©豆瓣","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>屠龙青年团</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期二</li><li><span>集数: </span>10</li><li><span>开始: </span>2012-07-17</li><li><span>类型: </span>深夜剧</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>日本</li><li><span>语言: </span>日语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>30分钟</li><li><span>首播国家: </span>日本</li><li><span>首播地区: </span>日本</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"上田诚","count":1},{"name":"安田章大","count":1},{"name":"2012","count":1},{"name":"特摄","count":1},{"name":"电视剧","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":711151,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/711151","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":711152,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/711152","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":711153,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/711153","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":711154,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/711154","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":711155,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/711155","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":711156,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/711156","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":711157,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/711157","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc